h4. Actor:
Customer.

h4. Description:
Name of use case represents its functionality.

h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks [Exchange House|guide:_ShowExchangeHousePlugin] option from top menu bar.
* Click "Report" sub menu from left menu.
* Click "Show Invoice" link.
* [Show Landing Page of "Invoice" Report For "Customer"|guide:ShowInvoiceForCustomer].
* Enter valid input.
* Click "PDF" icon of the upper right side of the page.
* System will show confirmation message of download.
* Actor clicks "Ok" button.
* Download "Invoice" Report For *Customer* in PDF Format.

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "Download invoice" privilege.
* Follow rules of validation:
{table}
 *Field* | *Input Type* | *Data Type* | *Rules* 
 Reference No | Text Box | Alpha Numeric | Required 
{table}


h4. Process:
* Download the report as PDF format.
* PDF header should show company logo and address.
* PDF report should show "Customer Copy" and "Bank Copy".

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** PDF Report will successfully download to user's computer.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].

